    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;Thus, only alphanumerics, the special characters “$-&lt;em&gt;.+!*’(),”, and reserved characters used for their reserved purposes may be used unencoded within a URL.&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc1738.txt&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;url rfc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;“只有字母和数字[0-9a-zA-Z]、一些特殊符号”$-&lt;/em&gt;.+!*’(),”[不包括双引号]、以及某些保留字，才可以不经过编码直接用于URL。”&lt;br&gt;
    
